CustomField.description: Holds value used in Approval process to determine if line should go to Pricing approval. Value is used to check if 'Net Rate Adjustment Percentage' is under the threshold and should go to Pricing approval queue.

CustomField.label: Net Rate Adjustment Percentage treshold
